gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Thunder 128, Trail Blazers 120
gameRecap.excerpt: Led by Shai Gilgeous-Alexander's 37 points and five assists, the Thunder defeated the Trail Blazers, 128-120. Jalen Williams added 31 points, four rebounds, three assists and three steals for the Thunder in the victory, while Anfernee Simons tallied 29 points (5-10 3pt. FG) and five assists for the Trail Blazers in the losing effort. The Thunder improve to 43-19 on the season, while the Trail Blazers fall to 17-44.
